&trans  &none                                         &kp KP_NUMBER_7                             &kp KP_NUMBER_8                           &kp KP_NUMBER_9           &kp CARET                    &kp F5           &kp PAGE_UP     &kp UP_ARROW    &kp PAGE_DOWN    &kp F11        &trans
